{"tid":2192232,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想向各位學弟妹/兄姐們 請教IELTS 問題","createTime":"2020-09-07T03:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T14:15:16.000Z","uid":372938,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"41615396ddb9dffc5e8b2cf6bd829d793beae321","tid":2192232,"uid":372938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:50:49.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟啱啱Grad 翻咗工都就快一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想的起心肝考翻個ielts for呢2年用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問問做ielts 13,14 2本夠唔夠用<br />\nListening 我就用youtube 啲個印度channel一個星期做3，4次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要想溫到reading, writing speaking... <br />\n我本人當年dse 得4 (3435) <br />\n做youtube 嘅listening 大約基本有6.5 每份都最少有28/40 個分range 大概28-33，34 <br />\n想穩定拎到grade 7 or above <br />\n但reading 就有啲難集中 有3篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次做得5.5 <br />\n想知點溫好。。。<br />\n而writing 就唯有每日睇一篇brand 7以上嘅範文 希望知啲人點寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSpeaking 就真係冇頭緒喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲可以教下小弟點溫好<br />\n想10月考 短時間係咪好難拎到 6.5/7？<br />\n想問電腦考同筆考有咩大分別？<br />\n我怕電腦考個keyboard 好大聲嘈到自己listening 同冇得highlight jot notes <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港警曱甴 我屌你老母啦 你啲後代生仔冇屎忽"},{"pid":"63305981e76400e348dc8d919037074a0ec5338f","tid":2192232,"uid":76922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:59:08.000Z","msg":"想知+1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102f1ae8b64f80e0118083be137ed679990f0265","tid":2192232,"uid":80696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:01:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afc4f78f9dfed0492ecc4352b3fc8a93c8a885d","tid":2192232,"uid":372938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e87dc7dc094f7b6f40e102dbb498092359c1f6","tid":2192232,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:25:00.000Z","msg":"吓 ielts? 遊戲嚟咋喎 唔洗識英文㗎 仲簡單過dse<br />\n裸考6.5 溫完7.5 你知題型 知佢點比分 就直接係搬字過紙咁濟"},{"pid":"0b6e8003e1607503a27b4a4c31edebe372525416","tid":2192232,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:25:37.000Z","msg":"睇下啲題型 marking s就夠"},{"pid":"061b19df35e81d6202e19f324d9a0c9f6975611b","tid":2192232,"uid":372938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家點溫speaking"},{"pid":"8ce786d4c4712e4af63c7913c26a7fe458de4704","tid":2192232,"uid":371107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"[警世]一年一度ielts傳銷騙局又嚟喇，切勿中伏！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192337\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192337</a>"},{"pid":"ef27c5f2228f8674cfa069673114f764af7bd5be","tid":2192232,"uid":372938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ce786d4c4712e4af63c7913c26a7fe458de4704","tid":2192232,"uid":371107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"[警世]一年一度ielts傳銷騙局又嚟喇，切勿中伏！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192337\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192337</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T07:55:34.000Z","msg":"Thanks <br />\n仲有冇多啲ielts分享"},{"pid":"703eaa7ce9ce